ISLAMABAD, Apr 5 (APP): Speaker National Assembly Raja Pervez Ashraf and Deputy Speaker Zahid Akram Durrani on Wednesday strongly condemned the brutal attack on Palestinian worshippers by Israeli Forces at Al-Aqsa mosque.
In a message, they prayed for those injured in the attack and urged the international community to take immediate action to halt aggression against Palestinians.
